{
  "name": "RPlog_Battle_of_the_Rocks",
  "title": "Pulled from the Asteroid Trap",
  "summary": "Captain Violet Allure's Corporate Sector light cruiser Venture is sprung from hyperspace into a Corellian asteroid field by a Twi'lek pirate hyper-trap, leaving her crippled and under fire from unmarked vessels. Viceprex Tyy'sun Eson, operating the carrier Remittance nearby, picks up her distress call and minijumps in to assist a fellow Corporate Sector ship. As Eson maneuvers the lumbering Remittance into the rocks to tractor the Venture clear, his ragtag fighter squadron under Gren Delede engages the pirates' TIEs and Hornets and destroys a boarding shuttle bound for the Venture. Delede exploits a known design flaw in the pirates' Carrack-class cruiser, calling concentrated warhead fire that cracks it open; with their capital ship ruined, the surviving pirates scatter and flee, and Eson tows the grateful Allure out of the field as the brief, bloody battle ends.",
